    "explanation":  "Konjunktiv I is used in B2 for indirect speech in news, academic texts, and formal communications. If a Konjunktiv-I form is identical to the Indikativ form, Konjunktiv II is often used instead to avoid ambiguity.",
    "examples":  [
                     "Der Minister sagte, die Lage sei ernst.",
                     "Experten behaupten, das Klima werde sich verändern.",
                     "Er sagte, er habe kein Geld."
